Variable Label: Planned Treatment Dose for Period xx
CDISC Notes: Subject-level identifier that represents the planned treatment dosage for period xx.

Variable Label: Actual Treatment Dose for Period xx
CDISC Notes: Subject-level identifier that represents the actual treatment dosage for period xx.

Variable Label: Units for Dose for Period xx
CDISC Notes: The units for DOSExxP and DOSExxA. It is permissible to use suffixes such as "P" and "A" if needed, with labels modified accordingly.
